---
layout: base.njk
title: 'about'
---

<article class="flow region">
    {% from 'macros/page-header.njk' import pageHeader %}
    {{ pageHeader({tag: 'malte b√§r', title: title}) }}

    <p>
        curious about the person behind the code? here's where you'll find my
        <a href="#experience">professional journey</a>,
        <a href="#education">educational background</a>, and the
        <a href="#interest">things that keep me excited about web development</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
        i believe that understanding a developer goes beyond just technical skills. my
        experiences and interests have shaped my approach to creating web solutions that
        are both effective and accessible. browse through the
        <a href="/projects">projects</a> to see what makes me tick.
    </p>
</article>

<article class="interest flow region">
    <h2 id="interest">interest</h2>

    <p>
        find below a list of my current go to references for the things i'm most
        interested in.
    </p>

    {% from 'macros/reveal-link-list.njk' import revealLinkList %}
    {{ revealLinkList({items: interests, name: 'interests', grid: 'true'}) }}
</article>

<article class="experience flow region">
    <h2 id="experience">experience</h2>

    <ul class="grid" data-layout="50-50">
        {% for job in experience %}
        <li>
            <article class="card flow">
                <footer>
                    <p>
                        <time datetime="{{ job.start }}">
                            {{ job.start | getLocaleDateString }}
                        </time>
                        -
                        <time datetime="{{ job.end }}">
                            {{ job.end | getLocaleDateString }}
                        </time>
                    </p>
                </footer>

                {% include 'svg/' + job.framework + '.svg' %}

                <header>
                    <h3>
                        <span>{{ job.role }}</span>
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        at
                        <a href="{{ job.website }}" target="_blank">
                            {{ job.location }}
                        </a>
                    </p>
                </header>

                <p>{{ job.description }}</p>
            </article>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</article>

<article class="education flow region">
    <h2 id="education">education</h2>

    <div class="education__table-container">
        <table>
            <tbody>
                {% for step in education %}
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p>
                            <time datetime="{{ step.start }}">
                                {{ step.start | getLocaleDateString }}
                            </time>
                            -
                            <time datetime="{{ step.end }}">
                                {{ step.end | getLocaleDateString }}
                            </time>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <h3>{{ step.type }}</h3>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>
                            at
                            <a href="{{ step.website }}" target="_blank">
                                {{ step.location }}
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>{{ step.description }}</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</article>
